title: The Matrix
description: "The Matrix" is a 1999 science fiction film with a virtual world theme. In the near future, Neo, a hacker, discovers the truth about the world he lives in which is just a matrix controlled by machines. He and the freedom fighters fight to free humans from the control of machines.
